									1,825,143 permits and has 746,430 active 
									licensees,<a href="#f105" style="text-decoration: none">[105]</a> constituting roughly 5.4% of 
									the state's population that is 21 years of 
									age or older.<a href="#f106" style="text-decoration: none">[106]</a><p>
