									rate has averaged 15% lower.<a href="#f108" style="text-decoration: none">[108]</a><p>
									&nbsp;<p>
									* From the outset of the Florida 
									right-to-carry law through July 31, 2010, 
									Florida has revoked 5,674 or 0.3% of all 
									issued permits. Of these:<p>
									&nbsp;<p class="indent">
									&bull; 522 permits were revoked for crimes 
									committed prior to licensure.<p class="indent">
